name: A.P. #704
description: This image is an animation still of the interactive audiovisual installation „Anima Perplexa“. A weightless form, which unfurls freely in the space and fluidly transforms into geometric or amorphous entities. Created with Max MSP Jitter. Resolution: 3456 × 2160px. Artist: Michel Winterberg, 2021, https://michelwintrberg.ch
